<normalizedToken originalValue="Río">Rio</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Paraguá">Paragua</normalizedToken>
basin around the Noel Kempff Park and in Brazil in the Pantanal. It is also extends along the 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Río">Rio</normalizedToken>
Paraguay into Paraguay and occurs in Minas Gerais and Bahia states in Brazil as well as in Venezuela and north to Costa Rica. It may be more widespread that the following records suggest.
